CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 17, 1956, pg. A10 reads: Garden Club Entertains - Knotty Pine Garden Club entertained scores of socialites Saturday at the Garden Center and presented as speaker, Wendell Wray. Standing is the president, Mrs. Hubert S. Stamps.  Seated are Mrs. Allen Rankin and Mrs. Elizabeth Strawder, chairman of the reception. - Harris PHoto."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Knotty Pine Garden Club members, from left, seated,  Mrs. Allen Rankin and Elizabeth Strawder; standing: Mrs. Hubert S. Stamps and guest speaker Wendell Wray, posed in Garden Center, another version
